reviewText: As much as I love the GREAT ONE, it was a dated documentary.
A little slow moving.  Also some footage from ultimate Gretzky.
great story of greatest hockey player ever
I was looking for something a little more in depth on Wayne.  It gives a good chronology, but even more on the Great One would have made this better!
Greatest Moments and Highlights of Wayne Gretzky the record breaker in Hockey History. This is a fast moving video that will keep your interest in amazement of the Great One.
HE WAS SLOW--HE WAS WEAK---DIDNT HAVE A GREAT SHOT---BUT THE GREATEST---GO FIGURE---AND A GREAT GUY---UNLIKE SO MUCH OF THE TRASH THAT PLAY PRO SPORTS TODAY. I BOYCOT MUCH TODAY
Awesome! Love it! I recommend this to everyone because it is awesome! It is a very cool item to have!
Very thorough background and trip through Gretzky's past.  You'll see his boyhood home where he practiced, talk with his dad and brother.  Just a great history of a terrific player's career.

What an amazing story The Great One has. From his days as a young boy through the end of his career with the New York Rangers. This DVD has it all. Perfect for anyone who loves hockey or great athletes.
Interesting enough disk, quite good replenishment of a collection of disks about best of the best hockey players of all times.
